      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "\"These outside agitators are just stirring up trouble where there ain't none,\" one might grumble, nursing his coffee. \"We got a way of doing things around here, and we ain't gonna let some meddling folks come in and mess up the natural order.\" Another might nod grimly, suggesting, \"We just need to make sure the folks understand their place, you know? Keep things settled so the business can keep turning.\"",
